data.description: Fantastic opportunity to own this outstanding horse property on a 1.1 acre lot! The charming remodeled home accommodates 3 beds, 2 baths, & a 2-car garage. Discover an open layout with wall cut-outs for a private yet airy feel! Formal dining area, neutral paint, tons of natural light, tile floors, and carpet t/out are some of the features you'll love. The kitchen boasts SS appliances, quartz counters, tile backsplash, a pantry, recessed lighting, white cabinetry, and an island w/breakfast bar. Double-door main bedroom features an ensuite w/dual vanities and two closets, one being a walk-in. Enjoy relaxing in the two covered patios! The HUGE backyard screams potential, offering a blank canvas for your horses, boats, trailers, or any idea you wish to bring to life. Don't miss it!
